Package shared.Model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AuthToken
    Authentication Token class that is in charge of creating tokens for users when they connect
    Event
    Class makes event objects that happen to a personID These events include birth, death, marriage, baptism etc.
    Person
    Class that creates a new personID and holds the data of a personID object include a set of event objects that has happen to this personID
    User
    Class contains the data for a user of the application including userName, password, email etc
